sources.title: The Hooked Generation (1968) BD RIP
sources.description: About a gang of dope peddlers who sail out to meet a Cuban boat. The trouble starts when they are forced to throw their narcotics overboard and are seen by a young couple.

metadata.Plot: A gang of dope peddlers sails out to meet a Cuban boat. The trouble starts when they are forced to throw their narcotics overboard and are seen by a young couple.
metadata.Writer: William Grefé, Quinn Morrison, Ray Preston
metadata.Actors: Jeremy Slate, Steve Alaimo, John Davis Chandler
